{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bbc8c41d2e","title":"关于罗印文同志被错划为右派的改正决定 (之一)","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8e64536fc6","index":0,"year":1979,"month":1,"day":23,"articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7ca44a3c40","type":"title","text":"关于罗印文同志被错划为右派的改正决定 (之一)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"6cec21b843","type":"paragraph","text":"罗印文同志一九五八年在本报被错划为右派分子，受到开除党籍、撤职降薪和监督劳动的处分。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"7a3e0a72eb","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央（1978）五十五号文件精神，对罗印文同志的问题进行了复查。罗印文在整风鸣放期间的言论不属右派言论。经报社党委讨论决定，对罗印文同志被错划为右派予以改正，撤销原有处分，恢复党籍，恢复原工资级别，收回报社安排工作。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"34c21b5c37","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共湖南日报社委员会（盖章）一九七九年元月二十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"a8b507c058","type":"subtitle","text":"关于罗印文同志被错划为右派的改正决定 （之二）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"7ed11c7481","type":"subtitle","text":"1979.02.11","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"4d4c6ad742","type":"paragraph","text":"罗印文同志在本报反右派运动中被划为右派分子，受到开除党籍，撤销原有职务，送农村监督劳动的处分。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"a0291ad2b1","type":"paragraph","text":"这次根据中共中央（1978）55号文件精神进行复查。罗印文同志原被划为右派分子属于错划，经研究予以改正，撤销原作处分，恢复党籍，恢复原工资级别行政17级，在错划右派期间应连续计算党龄、工龄。收回报社安排工作。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"ad6029fbea","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共湖南日报社委员会（盖章）一九七九年二月十一日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"},{"id":"cd1c531eda","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：罗印文《拒绝遗忘》，往事微痕丛刊。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e"}],"page":{"id":"aabbf0f27d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bbc8c41d2e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}